title: China Cafe
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Chinese, Delivery, Take-out, Asian, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. To-go and delivery only.  Has multiple vegan choices, some of which contain faux meat substitutes. Menu in the restaurant lists more vegan dishes than the online menu. Some of those dishes are mu shu vegetable, house deluxe vegetables, szechwan string beans and more.
